body:
I just saw this thread, so I figured I'd post here.
I'm RubberButt,  but anyone can call me Ryan as well.
Outside of Minecraft, I like to play instruments primarily. I play six instruments, which are electric bass, guitar, concert bass, drum kit, mandolin, and ukulele. 
I also enjoy listening to music. I enjoy most types of music, except for pure rap music.
If you ever wanna talk to me, feel free to pm me on Avicus or on the forums. I'll respond.
